extendedInfo.description: The application Equalizer FX allow you to improve sound for your android device.With Equalizer FX you able to control audio settings and effects for your device.Application include: - Equalizer. Is an audio filter to change the frequency envelope of the sound. - Bass boost. Is an audio effect to boost or amplify low frequencies of the sound. - Virtualization. Is an audio effect to virtualize audio channels. - 12 presets. Also you able to create your own presets.The application works with players and audio streaming services like VK, Pandora, Spotify, TuneIn Radio, etc.Note: Equalizer FX will not work with FM Radio.In full version the ad is removed.

reviews.title: 5 star worthy eq
reviews.comment: I hardly ever give out 5 stars on app ratings but once in awhile I come across a special one & this is one of them. I have tried this with - Tunein Pro, You Tube, MX Player with no issues. I like the \"blues\" setting on the eq & this really makes live performances sparkle on You Tube- even without the virtulizer turned on. I ditched the paid \"Equalizer\" app I had for this, much better off with this app IMO.
